kkable explanations—breaking down complex ideas so they're actually useful, not just impressive-sounding."]] ["h3" {:id "clojure-chronicles-(functional-programming-wisdom)"} [:<> "⚙️ Clojure Chronicles (Functional Programming Wisdom)"]] [:p [:<> "Exploring Clojure's design decisions and functional programming principles. Why immutability matters. Why simplicity beats complexity. What happens when you choose boring technology that actually scales. Lessons from languages designed by people who think deeply about software."]] ["h3" {:id "how-to-ai-(practical-ai-workflows)"} [:<> "🤖 How To AI (Practical AI Workflows)"]] [:p [:<> "The workflows, prompts, and patterns I actually use to leverage AI while building. Not hype, not theory—the specific ways I'm using AI tools to build faster. What works, what doesn't, what I learned from my mistakes."]] [:p [:strong [:<> "The common thread?"]] [:<> " These are all things I'm actively exploring while building Vade AI and living my life. This is my thinking out loud."]] [:p [:strong [:<> "What will I write about next week?"]] [:<> " I have no idea. That's the point."]] ["h2" {:id "the-three-reasons-i'm-doing-this"} [:<> "The Three Reasons I'm Doing This"]] [:p [:<> "I'm not going to pretend this is purely altruistic. I have clear goals:"]] ["h3" {:id "1.-satisfy-my-curiosity-(and-hold-myself-accountable)"} [:<> "1. Satisfy My Curiosity (And Hold Myself Accountable)"]] [:p [:<> "For the past four years, I've been stressed about the next paycheck. Worried about the depleting bank account. Carrying the weight of a small team and a growing family."]] [:p [:<> "I gave up the team. Found a job that lets me explore my curiosity while being useful to them. Now I can build without the constant panic of survival math."]] [:p [:strong [:<> "This is me choosing to enjoy the process instead of just grinding through it."]]] [:p [:<> "And doing it in public? That's my accountability mechanism. When I know people are watching, I show up. I do the work. I follow through."]] ["h3" {:id "2.-build-my-personal-brand-(the-honest-way)"} [:<> "2. Build My Personal Brand (The Honest Way)"]] [:p [:<> "Building an authentic brand is becoming equally difficult as building a product. Viral hooks win. Follower counts matter more than substance. But I believe there's still room for building a brand on genuine curiosity and real experience."]] [:p [:<> "This is my bet that authenticity still works."]] ["h3" {:id "3.-create-distribution-for-vade-ai"} [:<> "3. Create Distribution for Vade AI"]] [:p [:<> "When Vade AI launches, I need people who understand what I'm building and why it matters. People who'll give it an honest try and help me build it—instead of crickets when I make it live."]] [:p [:<> "Not because I pitched them, but because they've watched me build it in public. They've seen my thinking. They trust the process."]] [:p [:<> "Vade Bytes is that distribution engine."]] ["h2" {:id "the-restart-story-(why-now?)"} [:<> "The Restart Story (Why Now?)"]] [:p [:<> "For the past five years, I tried to bootstrap Vade AI with a small team. We had interns, an office in Bangalore, big dreams. My wife joined to handle operations. We even brought our newborn along for the journey."]] [:p [:<> "But the stress of a depleting bank account while building a family life took its toll. The weight of carrying everyone's livelihood on my shoulders became unbearable. The constant pressure to generate revenue while building something genuinely novel crushed my ability to think clearly."]] [:p [:strong [:<> "So I gave up the team."]]] [:p [:<> "Not the dream. Just the unsustainable way I was pursuing it."]] [:p [:<> "I found a job that lets me explore my curiosity and be useful to them. A job that gives me the mental space to build Vade AI properly, without panic, without the constant terror of \"how do I make payroll this month?\""]] [:p [:strong [:<> "This is my restart with a fresh perspective."]]] [:p [:<> "Vade Bytes is part of that restart. It's me choosing to:"]] [:ul [:li [:<> [:<> "Build my brand authentically (not through viral tricks)"]]] [:li [:<> [:<> "Create distribution for when Vade AI launches (by earning trust through sharing)"]]] [:li [:<> [:<> "Satisfy my curiosity consistently (instead of being consumed by survival stress)"]]] [:li [:<> [:<> "Actually enjoy the process (because what's the point otherwise?)"]]]] ["h2" {:id "join-me"} [:<> "Join Me"]] [:p [:strong [:<> "Vade Bytes is for builders."]]] [:p [:<> "People who are genuinely curious about a variety of topics. Who like to build things and learn by doing. Who are tired of the marketing fluff and performative content that dominates the internet."]] [:p [:<> "If that's you, subscribe."]] [:p [:<> "I'm restarting my journey with fresh perspective and sustainable pace. Building Vade AI while living a fulfilling life. Learning out loud. Sharing the receipts."]] [:p [:<> "No viral hooks. No follower count games. Just genuine curiosity and real building."]]], :nextjournal/render-opts {:id "tech-tides.vade-bytes-launch/markdown-5dthNrzUDUTDNutLqeheKTMeu22Q1G"}, :nextjournal/viewer {:name nextjournal.clerk.viewer/markdown-node-viewer, :render-fn #viewer-fn identity, :hash "5dsg4Bx9A9L7WvvCgamUoRtxUsmYCe"}} {:path [], :nextjournal/value [{:path [0], :nextjournal/value "(clerk/html\n [:div.mt-8.text-center\n  [:a.inline-block.px-6.py-3.bg-indigo-600.text-white.font-semibold.rounded-lg.hover:bg-indigo-700.transition\n   {:href \"https://vade.ai/bytes\"}\n   \"Subscribe to Vade Bytes →\"]])", :nextjournal/render-opts {:loc {:line 143, :end-line 147, :column 1, :end-column 34}, :id "tech-tides.vade-bytes-launch/anon-expr-5dtiXtApAcBpBA4AgDysqFLZrgbATV-code"}, :nextjournal/viewer {:name nextjournal.clerk.viewer/code-block-viewer, :render-fn #viewer-fn nextjournal.clerk.render/render-code-block, :hash "5dru1FUcVRTRrVKJFbNw4FG2wXmiwB"}} {:path [1], :nextjournal/value {:nextjournal/presented {:path [1], :nextjournal/value [:div.mt-8.tex